author: Linda Givetash and Salina Lee and Dawn Liu and Eric Baculinao and Associated Press
title: China is tracking asymptomatic cases. Why does that matter?
description: China began releasing data on asymptomatic coronavirus patients this week, a move experts say can inform how other countries respond to the global pandemic.
content:
China began to release data on asymptomatic coronavirus patients last week, a move experts say will help other countries respond to the pandemic and provide crucial insight into how the virus is spread.
